PrecisAmendments to the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS which will require that all air and hydraulic brake systems be equipped with automatic brake adjusters and that all air brake systems having external automatic adjusters and exposed pushrods be fitted with adjustment indicators.
